title: Windswept Dunes at White Sands
description: Undulating gypsum dunes reveal the intricate patterns carved by wind across White Sands National Park. The pristine white landscape stretches toward distant mountains under a crystalline sky, capturing the raw geometry and serene isolation of this otherworldly desert ecosystem.
location: Central Dune Field, White Sands National Park, New Mexico

title: Windswept Dunes of White Sands
description: Pristine gypsum dunes reveal intricate ripple patterns carved by wind, creating an otherworldly landscape of pure white against deep blue sky. The undulating terrain showcases the sculptural beauty of White Sands' dynamic desert environment.
location: White Sands National Park, New Mexico - Central Dune Field

title: Dunes and Desert Grasses
description: Delicate desert grasses anchor the pristine white gypsum landscape of White Sands, their golden stems creating a striking contrast against the stark dunes. This intimate study captures the quiet resilience of life in one of North America's most ethereal desert environments.
location: White Sands National Park, Alamogordo, New Mexico

title: Dunes and Desert Solitude
description: A solitary figure traverses the sculptural gypsum dunes of White Sands, where undulating white peaks frame vast, textured desert plains. This composition captures the sublime interplay between human presence and the immense, otherworldly landscape.
location: Central Dunes Region, White Sands National Park, New Mexico

title: Gypsum Dunes in Ethereal Light
description: A vast expanse of pure white gypsum dunes undulates across White Sands National Park, their sculptural forms casting subtle shadows that reveal the desert's otherworldly topography. This panoramic composition captures the pristine geometry and serene majesty of one of the world's most remarkable landscapes.
location: White Sands National Park, New Mexico - Central Dune Field

title: Gypsum Dunes in Stillness
description: Vast undulating gypsum dunes stretch toward distant ridges under a soft, luminous sky. The pristine white landscape reveals the subtle topography of wind-sculpted sand, creating a serene meditation on desert minimalism and geological majesty.
location: Central Dune Field, White Sands National Park, New Mexico

title: Gypsum Dunes and Mountain Silence
description: Rippling patterns of pristine gypsum sand stretch endlessly toward distant mountains in this meditative landscape. The interplay of light and shadow across the dunes creates a sense of infinite calm, inviting contemplation of nature's subtle geometry.
location: White Sands National Park, New Mexico - Central Dune Field

title: Solitary Figure in Gypsum Dunes
description: A lone figure stands atop the sculptural gypsum dunes of White Sands, silhouetted against distant mountains veiled in atmospheric haze. This meditative landscape captures the profound sense of isolation and scale within one of North America's most ethereal desert environments.
location: White Sands National Park, Central Dune Field

title: Dunes and Distant Mountains
description: A serene panoramic study of White Sands' undulating gypsum dunes meeting distant mountain ranges, where soft light and delicate atmospheric perspective create layers of minimalist beauty. The composition celebrates the raw geometry of wind-sculpted sand and the vast emptiness of this unique desert landscape.
location: Central Dunes, White Sands National Park, New Mexico
